show.title: Don't Get Your Heart Fluttering for Me
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://applinks.kukufm.com/2DdMKM8JRho1fFMLA
show.description: Rani, a young woman bound by an ancient pact and possessing mysterious powers, descends into the modern world to find her destined husband, Arjun. But Arjun is now a cold, powerful CEO, completely unaware of their connection. When Rani suddenly appears, claiming to be his wife based on a childhood marriage contract, Arjun dismisses her as delusional. However, dark forces plague Arjun's family, particularly his ailing grandfather, who seems afflicted by a sinister spell orchestrated by greedy relatives. As Rani uses her unique abilities to intervene, the lines between myth and reality blur. Faced with a world of magic he doesn't understand and a family he can't trust, will Arjun accept the impossible woman who claims his heart, or will darker schemes prevail?
